  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A cluster randomized experiment focused on testing the extent to which the
      organization-focused Implementation &amp; Sustainment Facilitation (ISF) strategy is an effective
      adjunct to the staff-focused Addiction Technology Transfer Center (ATTC) strategy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A cluster randomized experiment with 39 AIDS service organizations located across the United
      States. The overarching goal is to test the extent to which the organization-focused
      Implementation &amp; Sustainment Facilitation (ISF) strategy is an effective adjunct to the
      staff-focused Addiction Technology Transfer Center (ATTC) strategy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
